Package: shinystan
Title: Interactive Visual and Numerical Diagnostics and Posterior Analysis for 
  for Bayesian Models
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2015-08-07
Authors@R: c(person("Jonah", "Gabry", role = c("aut", "cre"),
